Maja Petrovic and Marko Miljevic dance “Merceditas” by Orquesta Simbolo Osmar Maderna, sung by Adolfo Rivas and Raúl Aldao, at the 12. Tango Tage Halle 2015 in Halle (Saale), Germany.
